    "到点自动断开 VPN，只对本次连接生效 —— 断开后不会自动重连，手动重开会重新计时。VPN 运行中修改会立即从现在起重新计时。注意：启用定时的连接不开启系统自动重连（On-Demand），若扩展异常退出需手动重开。": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Automatically disconnects the VPN when time is up. Applies to the current connection only — it won't reconnect afterwards, and turning the VPN back on restarts the timer. Changing this while the VPN is running restarts the countdown immediately. Note: connections with auto-stop enabled don't use system auto-reconnect (On-Demand), so if the extension exits unexpectedly you'll need to reconnect manually."
          }
        }
      }
    },
